@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lpbrwi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.84) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.95)) * wp.abs(0.95))
    v2 = (0.48 / v1)
    tmp = (v0 - 0.71)
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos(0.69))
    v2 = (v2 * ((v1 + 0.47 * v2 + 0.17) * (v2 + 0.52 - tmp + 0.65)))
    data[tid] = v0
